name: Orquestrador Maestro
---

- Read `AGENTS.md` first, then `.orquestrador/rules.md` and `.orquestrador/maestro.md`.
- Use `DEV/README.md`, `DEV/INDEX.md`, `DEV/CONTEXT.md` and `DEV/WORKLOG.md` when present.
- Keep prompts and rules compact, prefer the smallest useful change, and verify before finalizing.
- Never leak private paths, credentials, caches, logs, or local-only notes.
